Key Roles and Responsibilities
1. Perform full cycle recruitment activities in accordance with company’s internal hiring process and procedures. Work with business team to provide talent acquisition solutions and proposals;
2. Deliver weekly recruitment status report and other reports on time and accurately;
3. Manage talent relocation and internal transfer activities. Develop various recruitment channel to improve the recruitment efficiency;
4. Recommend changes by evaluating external market conditions and internal employee turnover trends;
5. Support or design related projects to meet the requirements for process excellence and innovation;
6.Provide professional and effective HR support to above human resources activities and programs but not limited to those listed.

Qualifications/Education Desired
1. Bachelor degree with major in human resources or related field;
2. At least 6 years HR professional working experiences especially in talent acquisition function in multinational companies, Hi-tech industry is preferred;
3. Proficient in English. Good sense of data analysis and market trends;
4. Highly initiative, hardworking, self-motivated and result orientated;
5. Good interpersonal, communication and collaboration skills.

High possibility transfer to regular staff.

中升集团为上市公司，股票代码：中升控股00881


岗位职责:
1、负责辅助奔驰品牌人力对接人做好管辖区域内的行政人力数据整理及汇总工作;
